Polaris Bank has said it will delight existing and new customers during the Valentine season with exciting rewards via a campaign themed ‘Polaris Purple Reward’. According to a statement by the bank, existing and prospective customers stood a chance to enjoy a reward of N5,000 worth of data in the Valentine campaign. It added that 50 customers with the highest cumulative transaction value within the period would be rewarded. The statement said the criteria for qualifying for the reward would be premised on using the bank’s VULTe app to either pay bills, perform interbank transactions or airtime purchases. It said winners would be announced on the bank’s Instagram page. Polaris Bank’s Group Head, Strategic Brand Management, Nduneche Ezurike, who announced the Valentine reward said, “The reward campaign which will run from February 8 to 14 2023, is another opportunity to show love to our esteemed customers by rewarding their loyalty for banking with us. “Valentine is known globally as a season of love and sharing, and as a Bank which puts its customers at the centre of everything we do, we deemed it fit to delight them with exciting rewards in commemoration of the Valentine season.”